NK031(ki)005:0: rdzogs chen sems sde brgyud pa'i gsol 'debs byin rlabs kyi dga' ston bzhugs so //

NK031(ki)005:5: gsol ba 'debs so byin gyis brlab tu gsol //

NK031(ki)005:25: gsol ba 'debs so byin gyis brlab tu gsol //

NK031(ki)005:148: gsol ba 'debs so byin gyis brlab tu gsol //

NK031(ki)005:174: mi 'gyur gzhi dbyings nama mkha'i rdo rje las //
NK031(ki)005:175: tshe dbang grub pa'i rgyal sar mnga' bsgyur ba //

NK031(ki)005:177: gsol ba 'debs so byin gyis brlab tu gsol //

NK031(ki)005:232: rdzogs pa chen po sems phyogs kyi bla ma brgyud
NK031(ki)005:233: pa la gsol ba 'debs pa byin rlabs kyi dga'
NK031(ki)005:235: rje btsun bla ma de dag la mi phyed pa dang /
NK031(ki)005:238: dad pa gsum dang ldan pa blo gros rgyal mtshan dpal bzang pos sbyar ba'o ////
NK031(ki)005:240: pan chen bi ma las bsgyur ba'i phyi 'gyur bcu gsum dang sems sde nyer gcig /

NK031(ki)005:248: mnga' ris mdo khams yan chad du so sor brgyud lugs mtha' yas yod mod kyang /
NK031(ki)005:251: dbus gtsang 'dres ma dang gsum du bzhag pa las /

NK031(ki)005:254: yang dbus gtsang 'dres ma'i brgyud lugs gcig la zur chung nas glan sh+aakya bzang po /
NK031(ki)005:258: mnyam med dam pa sh+aaka rgyal /
NK031(ki)005:259: bla ma lha rje chen po /
NK031(ki)005:261: sangs rgyas smyon ston bla ma /
NK031(ki)005:263: skye med dam pa sangs rgyas /
NK031(ki)005:264: skyes mchog sprul sku chen po /
NK031(ki)005:265: chos rgyal mnga' ris pan chen /
NK031(ki)005:267: mkhan chen mdzes pa'i rgyal mtshan /
NK031(ki)005:268: rtogs ldan chos dpal bzang po /
NK031(ki)005:269: mkhan chen blo gros rta nag thub bstan gyi mkhan po /
NK031(ki)005:273: sog zlog pa blo gros rgyal mtshan /
NK031(ki)005:274: de man chod gong gi gsol 'debs ltar dang /
NK031(ki)005:275: brgyud tshul gzhan thob yig ltar ro //
